Brightness overlay


—

7. WEATHER REACTIVE UI (Future Phase)



The entire UI atmosphere changes based on real-time weather data.

Examples:

Rain → darker theme, rain particles, deeper glass effect

Snow → white particles, frosted blur intensifies

Night → star field activated

Thunderstorm → subtle lightning flashes

Sunny → warm glow particles


This is not a widget feature — it is full atmosphere transformation.

—

8. ECLIPSE ISLAND (Dynamic Island Concept)



A pill-shaped interactive element at the top of the screen.

Behavior:

Idle → small animated Eclipse logo

Music → expands with album art and controls

Download → shows progress

Search → loading animation

Timer → countdown display

Weather alert → expands with icon


Goal: Bring dynamic interaction style to Android in a browser environment.

—

