10. COMMUNITY & PROFILE SYSTEM (Future)



Eclipse Profile:

Username

Bio

Animated banner

Custom badges

Showcase layouts


Eclipse Cloud:

Share layout JSON

Preview designs

Apply with one tap

Rate and comment

