# ECLIPSE BROWSER — COMPLETE MASTER ROADMAP

---

## THE VISION

The only mobile browser where you completely own everything. Your UI. Your search experience. Your widgets. Your privacy. Better than any PC browser extension. Free forever. For everyone.

---

## CORE PHILOSOPHY

**Three promises to every user**
- Your data never leaves your device without your permission. Ever.
- Everything is free. No premium tier. No paid features. Ever.
- You own your experience completely. We just give you the canvas.

---

## TECHNOLOGY STACK — ALL FREE FOREVER

| Component | Technology | Hosting | Cost | Signup Needed |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Browser engine | Android WebView | On device | Free | Nothing |
| Search | SearXNG | Render.com | Free | GitHub account |
| AI features | Groq API | Their servers | Free | Email only |
| Community layouts | Supabase | Their servers | Free | Email only |
| Backend API | Cloudflare Workers | Their servers | Free | Email only |
| Future AI | Hugging Face | Their servers | Free | Email only |
| User data | Device localStorage | On device | Free | Nothing |

**Total cost — Zero rupees. Forever.**

