**Expands for —**
- Music playing — album art + song name + controls expand from pill
- Download happening — progress bar expands from pill
- Search running — loading animation in pill
- Weather alert — weather icon expands
- Timer running — countdown shows in pill
- Notification — expands briefly then shrinks back

All animated. All smooth. All feeling like it belongs there.

Android users have never had this. Eclipse gives it to them free.

